      "content": "it's not just stress though. it's like... they're right. they've said such horrible things about me that i actually started believing it. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize myself anymore. i'm just a joke to everyone. why would anyone even want to be around someone like me? it feels like i'm just taking up space that i don't even deserve.",
